#	 About VirtualPlacos

VirtualPlacos simulates a simple indoor garden with hardware and 
openplacOS driver

it has two sensor :
	- indoor temperature
	- outdoor temperature

and two effectors 
	- ligth
	- fan

When light is on, the indoor temperature increase. Conversely, when fan 
is on the indoor temperature decrease.
When light and fan are on, the indoor temperature stabilizes itself 
according to the time constants define in config file.

Driver offers different objects linked to the VirtualPlacos state.

- Pin_1 ==> Indoor Temperature
- Pin_2 ==> Outdoor Temperature
- Pin_3 ==> Light
- Pin_4 ==> fan

see config.yaml for further information. 


